                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-167-off870 t18220417-167-cd871"></join>, one gown, value 6 s., two petticoats, value 2 s., one pair of stays, value 2 s., one pair of stockings, value 1 s., one pair of boots, value 2 s., one handkerchief, value 6 d., one bonnet, value 4 s., one purse, value 1 d., one thimble, 1 d., and seventeen shillings in money
